  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims at evaluating the diagnostic efficacy of Gadobutrol versus Gadobenate
      dimeglumine at similar dose of 0.1mmol/kg for assessment of myocardial infarction by delayed
      enhancement cardiac Magnetic Resonance Imaging
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
